          <div class="cta-copy">
            <h4>Don't want to evaluate 12 tools yourself?</h4>
            <p>Tell us your site and your top 5 keywords. We will tell you in 24 hours which generator fits — and whether you should buy software at all or let someone <strong>run blog SEO for you</strong>.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="cta-action">
            <a href="/demo/" class="cta-btn-inline">Book my strategy call <span>→</span></a>
            <span class="cta-meta">30-min · No pitch</span>
          </div>
        </div>

